493.
1095Hetuṃ anāgatārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu anāgatārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
1096Nahetuṃ anāgatārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu anāgatārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
1097Hetuṃ anāgatārammaṇañca nahetuṃ anāgatārammaṇañca dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu anāgatārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
494.
1098Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava…pe…  kamme nava…pe…  avigate nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
